snippet.title: BlazeRush - Official Teaser Trailer | PS3
snippet.description:
Blaze Rush is a dynamic vehicular combat game with no health, no leveling and no brakes!

The game will be available on PS3 and PC this november.    

http://blazerush.com/?lang=en
